Big Brother Naija 2019 housemate, Mercy, has revealed that she would like to have a relationship with housemate, Ike after the show. Mercy said this during her diary session on Tuesday. Speaking to Big Brother, she added she would love to be in a relationship with Ike after the “Pepper Dem” edition. When asked if she is interested in anyone in the house, Mercy said: “Yes Ike, but I want to slow it down for now because I’ve been through a lot in my past relationships. “But he is one guy I’ll love to be with after the house.” Meanwhile, Mercy is up for eviction this week and may likely go home on Sunday alongside SirDee, Tacha, Ella and KimOprah